AddressInfo.Title: 1851 IONITY DC by EF РЦ Промінь

GeneralComments: To connect your EV to a charging station, please download the EcoFactor mobile App with the following links:  for iOS users: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ecofactor-network/id1438716797?ls=1  for Android users: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=eu.ecofactor&hl=en  After registering in the App you will have the following features available: - Start / stop of the charging station; - View charging station status (busy / free); - Reviewing and replenishing your balance; - View the charging process of your EV and the amount of electricity consumed, as well as many other convenient features.
